{"tid":1052353,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"會長佩雷斯已經打電話找施丹回歸,施丹拒絕重返皇馬","createTime":"2019-03-08T08:46:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T10:11:07.000Z","uid":173952,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"314aa82b798195f550410d8f5a75ad04b34d0bc5","tid":1052353,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T08:46:26.000Z","msg":"施丹去季完成歐聯3連霸之後轉身離開，今季皇馬成績大走樣，歐聯又不敵阿積士出局，度過了傷心的一季。<br />\n雖然球會邀請施丹回巢，但已經被拒絕。前會長卡達朗說：「我知道會長佩雷斯已經打電話找施丹回歸，但他拒絕了，他說最少不是現在。但是，他都留下伏線，有可能6月再考慮。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81cfbe85c6d08b0736846f338c990f3dc70f34dc","tid":1052353,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T08:51:56.000Z","msg":"施丹去曼聯嘛<br />\n<br />\n之前d獌狗吹到約都簽好"},{"pid":"01719f8462d110562d052f022b408e6d667869db","tid":1052353,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81cfbe85c6d08b0736846f338c990f3dc70f34dc","tid":1052353,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T08:51:56.000Z","msg":"施丹去曼聯嘛<br />\n<br />\n之前d獌狗吹到約都簽好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T08:53:59.000Z","msg":"C朗打電話比我,話佢下季黎祖記BO"},{"pid":"53995a9cf685820d201808ef9d209bc9eb064ca3","tid":1052353,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81cfbe85c6d08b0736846f338c990f3dc70f34dc","tid":1052353,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T08:51:56.000Z","msg":"施丹去曼聯嘛<br />\n<br />\n之前d獌狗吹到約都簽好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T08:58:21.000Z","msg":"系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />枉SO SIR咁熱心"},{"pid":"fb00a84b92a294e3043c6d64584d569a059f9621","tid":1052353,"uid":8636,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T08:59:41.000Z","msg":"地中海佬撚有料tune番隊波咩"},{"pid":"2c20ac61d06676cf46eddc5a71212cd53d2376c9","tid":1052353,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T09:32:40.000Z","msg":"會長同會員一樣咁肉酸